entries.femaleVariant: Shhh! It musn't blink! Or the mask will fall off!
It mustn't tell them it's an android. They don't like androids.
Heh, oh, but I simply don't know how to dance!
Ooh! And a one, and a two…
Hello. We want to report a kidnapping.
Us, of course… Two times… Last Friday and tomorrow at three… Well, they replaced us with an android, so nobody noticed.
We will tell you who… Fairies… You can't hurt them… They're bad to the bone … Or aluminum… Ours was made of aluminum.
It's a mixup! We aren't a bloodhound!
But – but we really can't dance! They took our legs!
You mustn't follow us. The bloodhounds will track us… and take us back.
Her light isn't bright. She must escape. She won't succeed.
entries.maleVariant: His light isn't bright. He must escape. He won't succeed.
